" (<Visual>:ctt<Tab>) copy multiline stmt to be use in tridactyl exmode. {{{1 }}}
" vim9 command! -buffer -range CopyToTridactyl @" = getline(<line1>, <line2>)->map((_, line) => line->substitute('[\\]$', '', ''))->join(' ') | feedkeys("\<Space>y")
